  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Story</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >When <strong>Jack Frost</strong> infiltrates Santa's Workshop and steals the<strong> 6 Grand Presents</strong> the fate of the season hangs in the balance! Join <strong>Lux</strong> the red nosed reindeer<strong> </strong>and his friends in their struggle to defeat Jack Frost's forces and prevent an <strong>Eternal Winter</strong>!  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In this cool <strong>Adventure RPG</strong> Fight foes in frantic turn based battles with real-time elements and action commands! Use your Reindeer Abilities in and out of battle to overcome Jack Frost and his elite henchmen, retrieve the 6 Grand Presents and return balance to the season!<br>  </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Be a Deer!</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Exploration with Platforming! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1946170/extras/ac9cb9e20cbcdf026bcbdd6e66a05425.poster.avif?t=1759507609\" width=470 height=264 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1946170/extras/ac9cb9e20cbcdf026bcbdd6e66a05425.webm?t=1759507609\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1946170/extras/ac9cb9e20cbcdf026bcbdd6e66a05425.mp4?t=1759507609\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Turn based battles with Action Commands! Time your button presses to maximise damage!   <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1946170/extras/9e15c446b8bc0372d29c87d9b2256eae.poster.avif?t=1759507609\" width=470 height=264 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1946170/extras/9e15c446b8bc0372d29c87d9b2256eae.webm?t=1759507609\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1946170/extras/9e15c446b8bc0372d29c87d9b2256eae.mp4?t=1759507609\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Evade enemy attacks in real time, Use Z-Skills to strike back during their turn!    <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1946170/extras/ea85adf8fe857f1d93308b1af94126ae.poster.avif?t=1759507609\" width=470 height=264 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1946170/extras/ea85adf8fe857f1d93308b1af94126ae.webm?t=1759507609\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1946170/extras/ea85adf8fe857f1d93308b1af94126ae.mp4?t=1759507609\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Solve puzzles using your magical red-nose to fire lasers or charge with your antlers to break straight through obstacles!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  Saddle up! Collect equipment and magical baubles to boost your party's stats and unlock new skills in battle! </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  Meet a cast of 100's of cool, cute and crude characters!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >An exciting 6-chapter adventure awaits in <strong>Reindeer Story</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Reindeer Story</strong> draws inspiration from a varied set of classic and modern RPGs including Paper Mario, Mario & Luigi, Final Fantasy 1-9 and Deltarune. It will feature a 10+ hour main story line, New Game+ and a lot of optional content and secrets to uncover that will give you reasons to keep coming back!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >They say the story of the red nose reindeer captured the hearts of millions... This game is a fun and surprising adventure that will be great to play every Winter as a tradition!</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Story</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >When <strong>Jack Frost</strong> infiltrates Santa's Workshop and steals the<strong> 6 Grand Presents</strong> the fate of the season hangs in the balance! Join <strong>Lux</strong> the red nosed reindeer<strong> </strong>and his friends in their struggle to defeat Jack Frost's forces and prevent an <strong>Eternal Winter</strong>!  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In this cool <strong>Adventure RPG</strong> Fight foes in frantic turn based battles with real-time elements and action commands! Use your Reindeer Abilities in and out of battle to overcome Jack Frost and his elite henchmen, retrieve the 6 Grand Presents and return balance to the season!<br>  </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Be a Deer!</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Exploration with Platforming! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1946170/extras/ac9cb9e20cbcdf026bcbdd6e66a05425.poster.avif?t=1759507609\" width=470 height=264 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1946170/extras/ac9cb9e20cbcdf026bcbdd6e66a05425.webm?t=1759507609\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1946170/extras/ac9cb9e20cbcdf026bcbdd6e66a05425.mp4?t=1759507609\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Turn based battles with Action Commands! Time your button presses to maximise damage!   <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1946170/extras/9e15c446b8bc0372d29c87d9b2256eae.poster.avif?t=1759507609\" width=470 height=264 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1946170/extras/9e15c446b8bc0372d29c87d9b2256eae.webm?t=1759507609\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1946170/extras/9e15c446b8bc0372d29c87d9b2256eae.mp4?t=1759507609\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Evade enemy attacks in real time, Use Z-Skills to strike back during their turn!    <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1946170/extras/ea85adf8fe857f1d93308b1af94126ae.poster.avif?t=1759507609\" width=470 height=264 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1946170/extras/ea85adf8fe857f1d93308b1af94126ae.webm?t=1759507609\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1946170/extras/ea85adf8fe857f1d93308b1af94126ae.mp4?t=1759507609\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Solve puzzles using your magical red-nose to fire lasers or charge with your antlers to break straight through obstacles!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  Saddle up! Collect equipment and magical baubles to boost your party's stats and unlock new skills in battle! </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  Meet a cast of 100's of cool, cute and crude characters!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >An exciting 6-chapter adventure awaits in <strong>Reindeer Story</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Reindeer Story</strong> draws inspiration from a varied set of classic and modern RPGs including Paper Mario, Mario & Luigi, Final Fantasy 1-9 and Deltarune. It will feature a 10+ hour main story line, New Game+ and a lot of optional content and secrets to uncover that will give you reasons to keep coming back!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >They say the story of the red nose reindeer captured the hearts of millions... This game is a fun and surprising adventure that will be great to play every Winter as a tradition!</p>",
